y and you didn't pass uid output directory with -djunit.platform.listeners.uid.tracking.output.dir=<path>.\\n[junit-platform-native] WARNING: Using test-ids from default Gradle project location:/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge8/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/4727-1f9d9187/tests/src/com.google.appengine/appengine-api-1.0-sdk/2.0.32/build/test-results/test/testlist\\n[junit-platform-native] Running in 'test listener' mode using files matching pattern [junit-platform-unique-ids*] found in folder [/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge8/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/4727-1f9d9187/tests/src/com.google.appengine/appengine-api-1.0-sdk/2.0.32/build/test-results/test/testlist] and its subfolders.\\nJUnit Platform on Native Image - report\\n----------------------------------------\\n\\ncom_google_appengine.appengine_api_1_0_sdk.Appengine_api_1_0_sdkTest > datastoreKeysEntitiesPropertiesAndQueriesRoundTrip() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\ncom_google_appengine.appengine_api_1_0_sdk.Appengine_api_1_0_sdkTest > mailUsersMemcacheBlobstoreCapabilitiesAndImagesExposeValueState() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\ncom_google_appengine.appengine_api_1_0_sdk.Appengine_api_1_0_sdkTest > appIdentityServiceParsesFullApplicationIds() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\ncom_google_appengine.appengine_api_1_0_sdk.Appengine_api_1_0_sdkTest > namespaceManagerStoresValidNamespacesOnCurrentRequest() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\ncom_google_appengine.appengine_api_1_0_sdk.Appengine_api_1_0_sdkTest > urlFetchRequestsResponsesAndOptionsExposeHttpState() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\ncom_google_appengine.appengine_api_1_0_sdk.Appengine_api_1_0_sdkTest > searchDocumentsFieldsFacetsAndQueryOptionsAreComposable() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\ncom_google_appengine.appengine_api_1_0_sdk.Appengine_api_1_0_sdkTest > taskQueueOptionsBuildHttpAndPullQueueRequests() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\ncom_google_appengine.appengine_api_1_0_sdk.Appengine_api_1_0_sdkTest > apiProxyRoutesSynchronousAndAsynchronousCallsThroughDelegate() SUCCESSFUL\\n\\ncom_goog